{"word":"H7495 - רָפָא - râphâʼ - raw-faw' - Cure","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">רָפָא</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>râphâʼ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>raw-faw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Cure"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சுகமாகுதல், குணப்படு, குணமாக்கு நலமாயிரு, அநுகூலம் செய், ஷேமத்தைக் கொடு, ஆற்று, வைத்திய வைத்தியர், பரிகாரி, சொஸ்தமாகு, நிவிர்த்தியாகு, ஆரோக்கியமாகு, ஆறு செப்பனிடப்படு, பழுதுபார், ஆற்றிக்கொள்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to heal, to make healthful"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) to heal"},{"paragraph":"1) of God"},{"paragraph":"2) a healer, a physician (of men)"},{"paragraph":"3) used of the hurts of nations involving restored favor (figurative)"},{"paragraph":"4) usedof individual distresses (figurative)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Niphal) to be healed"},{"paragraph":"1) literal (used of persons)"},{"paragraph":"2) used of water, pottery"},{"paragraph":"3) used of national hurts (figurative)"},{"paragraph":"4) usedof personal distress (figurative)"},{"paragraph":"c) (Piel) to heal"},{"paragraph":"1) literal"},{"paragraph":"2) used of national defects or hurts (figurative)"},{"paragraph":"d) (Hithpael) in order to get healed (infinitive)"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; properly to <i>mend</i> (by stitching), that is, (figuratively) to <i>cure</i>: - cure, (cause to) heal, physician, repair, X thoroughly, make whole. See <a href=\"#/H7503 - רָפָה - râphâh - raw-faw'/7503\">H7503</a>."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3416 - יִרְפְּאֵל - Yirpᵉʼêl - yir-peh-ale'/3416\">H3416</a>, <a href=\"#/H4832 - מַרְפֵּא - marpêʼ - mar-pay'/4832\">H4832</a>, <a href=\"#/H7495 - רָפָא - râphâʼ - raw-faw'/7495\">H7495</a>, <a href=\"#/H7498 - רָפָא - Râphâʼ - raw-faw'/7498\">H7498</a>, <a href=\"#/H7499 - רְפֻאָה - rᵉphuʼâh - ref-oo-aw'/7499\">H7499</a>, <a href=\"#/H7500 - רִפְאוּת - riphʼûwth - rif-ooth'/7500\">H7500</a>, <a href=\"#/H7501 - רְפָאֵל - Rᵉphâʼêl - ref-aw-ale'/7501\">H7501</a>, <a href=\"#/H7505 - רָפוּא - Râphûwʼ - raw-foo'/7505\">H7505</a>, <a href=\"#/H7509 - רְפָיָה - Rᵉphâyâh - ref-aw-yaw'/7509\">H7509</a>"}]}